{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41795753b9","title":"139号犯人狱中报告（与194号谈话）","origin":"李辉整理《赵丹自述》，大象出版社，2003年1月第一版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a5d2fb451","index":0,"year":1969,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"41795753b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"b5d30cfdb0","name":"赵丹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2efa4cb859","type":"title","text":"139号犯人狱中报告（与194号谈话）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"41c6cfd1df","type":"authors","text":"赵丹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"45a61da24d","type":"paragraph","text":"今天劳动的时候，我与194号谈了话。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"4e6a5d6c4e","type":"paragraph","text":"我问他，专案组提审他时，讲了点外面的形势没有？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"a90c94d58f","type":"paragraph","text":"他回答说:“专案组交代政策，说只要交代得好，这里面的人也可以有做人民内部矛盾来处理的，不一定带帽子才放出去。”","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"2963807b80","type":"paragraph","text":"他又说:“态度很重要。”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"94a18b075d","type":"paragraph","text":"我说:“我的事坏就坏在态度上，常常为了这一点枝枝节节的小事，甚至一言一语，就和专案组顶起嘴来了！”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"1c2112311b","type":"paragraph","text":"他说:“过去我也顶过嘴，事后，后悔得不得了！”","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"46adfa6995","type":"paragraph","text":"正在此时，解放军同志来对我们进行警告和教育了。我们没再谈别的，尤其是个人的案情，我们彼此从未交谈过。直到现在，他叫什么名字、在哪儿工作，我都不晓得。当然，他知道我是干电影的赵丹。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"532b94c9be","type":"paragraph","text":" 139","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"},{"id":"3e4ee30995","type":"appellation","text":"一九六九年十一月二十二日","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9"}],"page":{"id":"c4f18d525c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41795753b9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}